  }, "v24"), mdx("p", null, "Ng\xE0i \u0111\xE3 gi\u1EEF l\u1EDDi h\u1EE9a c\xF9ng cha t\xF4i l\xE0 \u0110a-v\xEDt, k\u1EBB t\xF4i t\u1EDB Ng\xE0i. Mi\u1EC7ng Ng\xE0i \u0111\xE3 h\u1EE9a v\xE0 h\xF4m nay tay Ng\xE0i \u0111\xE3 th\u1EF1c hi\u1EC7n l\u1EDDi h\u1EE9a \u0111\xF3. "), mdx("h6", {
