  }, "v30"), mdx("p", null, "Xin h\xE3y nghe l\u1EDDi c\u1EA7u nguy\u1EC7n c\u1EE7a t\xF4i c\xF9ng l\u1EDDi c\u1EA7u nguy\u1EC7n c\u1EE7a \xCDt-ra-en, d\xE2n Ng\xE0i khi ch\xFAng t\xF4i h\u01B0\u1EDBng v\u1EC1 \u0111\u1EC1n th\u1EDD n\u1EA7y m\xE0 c\u1EA7u nguy\u1EC7n. T\u1EEB n\u01A1i \u1EDF c\u1EE7a Ng\xE0i tr\xEAn tr\u1EDDi xin h\xE3y nghe v\xE0 tha th\u1EE9 cho ch\xFAng t\xF4i. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v31"
  }, "v31"), mdx("p", null, "N\u1EBFu ai l\xE0m t\u1ED5n h\u1EA1i ng\u01B0\u1EDDi kh\xE1c v\xE0 b\u1ECB mang \u0111\u1EBFn b\xE0n th\u1EDD c\u1EE7a \u0111\u1EC1n th\u1EDD n\u1EA7y. N\u1EBFu ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111\xF3 th\u1EC1 r\u1EB1ng m\xECnh ho\xE0n to\xE0n v\xF4 t\u1ED9i, "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v32"
  }, "v32"), mdx("p", null, "th\xEC xin CH\xDAA t\u1EEB tr\u1EDDi h\xE3y nghe. Xin ph\xE2n x\u1EED v\u1EE5 \u0111\xF3, tr\u1EEBng ph\u1EA1t k\u1EBB c\xF3 t\u1ED9i, nh\u01B0ng tuy\xEAn b\u1ED1 k\u1EBB v\xF4 t\u1ED9i \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c tr\u1EAFng \xE1n. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v33"
  }, "v33"), mdx("p", null, "Khi \xCDt-ra-en, d\xE2n CH\xDAA, ph\u1EA1m t\u1ED9i c\xF9ng Ng\xE0i v\xE0 b\u1ECB k\u1EBB th\xF9 \u0111\xE1nh b\u1EA1i. N\u1EBFu h\u1ECD tr\u1EDF l\u1EA1i c\xF9ng Ng\xE0i, ca ng\u1EE3i v\xE0 c\u1EA7u nguy\u1EC7n c\xF9ng CH\xDAA trong \u0111\u1EC1n th\u1EDD n\u1EA7y, "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v34"
  }, "v34"), mdx("p", null, "th\xEC xin Ng\xE0i t\u1EEB tr\u1EDDi h\xE3y nghe. H\xE3y tha t\u1ED9i cho h\u1ECD v\xE0 mang h\u1ECD tr\u1EDF v\u1EC1 x\u1EE9 m\xE0 Ng\xE0i ban cho t\u1ED5 ti\xEAn h\u1ECD. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v35"
